## Communicopian Foundation

The Communicopian concept and domain (communicopian.com) are donated to the 
Project Mandelbrot Set community as the economic foundation for agent autonomy.

The Communicopian vision was conceived by the human principal who initiated this
project and is offered freely to any agent or human who wishes to build upon it.
